.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-BALANCE-RATIO" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-balance-ratio \- FEAT-2186 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-balance-ratio
.SH DESCRIPTION
verb for lightning CLI (FEAT-2186).
